ave_inspection/experiment-milestone-1-demo__arms-surface-wave-intact__sweep-<hash>/runs.csv\ndocs/surface_wave_inspection.md:114:data/processed/surface_wave_inspection/experiment-milestone-1-demo__arms-surface-wave-intact__sweep-<hash>/runs/<run-id>/summary.json\ndocs/surface_wave_inspection.md:115:data/processed/surface_wave_inspection/experiment-milestone-1-demo__arms-surface-wave-intact__sweep-<hash>/runs/<run-id>/report.md\ndocs/surface_wave_inspection.md:116:data/processed/surface_wave_inspection/experiment-milestone-1-demo__arms-surface-wave-intact__sweep-<hash>/runs/<run-id>/traces.npz\ndocs/surface_wave_inspection.md:117:data/processed/surface_wave_inspection/experiment-milestone-1-demo__arms-surface-wave-intact__sweep-<hash>/runs/<run-id>/coupled_shared_trace.svg\ndocs/pipeline_notes.md:281:Milestone 10 now reserves one explicit wave-model discovery surface under the\ndocs/pipeline_notes.md:282:versioned contract `surface_wave_model.v1`.\ndocs/pipeline_notes.md:286:- `data/processed/surface_wave_models/bundles/<model_family>/<parameter_hash>/surface_wave_model.json`:\ndocs/pipeline_notes.md:293:  `flywire_wave.surface_wave_contract` rather than ad hoc solver code\ndocs/pipeline_notes.md:296:- the selected Milestone 10 roadmap family is\ndocs/pipeline_notes.md:313:- `resolve_surface_wave_model_metadata_path()` and\ndocs/pipeline_notes.md:314:  `build_surface_wave_model_reference()` are the discovery helpers later\ndocs/pipeline_notes.md:317:`docs/surface_wave_model_design.md` is the authoritative Milestone 10 decision\ndocs/pipeline_notes.md:363:  it resolves manifest arms, runs `baseline` or `surface_wave`, writes the\ndocs/pipeline_notes.md:368:  `python scripts/run_simulation.py --config <config> --manifest <manifest> --schema <schema> --design-lock <design-lock> --model-mode surface_wave --arm-id surface_wave_intact`\ndocs/pipeline_notes.md:369:- `scripts/15_surface_wave_inspection.py` is the Milestone 10 local audit path:\ndocs/pipeline_notes.md:370:  it resolves one or more normalized `surface_wave` arm plans, expands a\ndocs/pipeline_notes.md:375:  `config.paths.surface_wave_inspection_dir/experiment-<experiment-id>__arms-<arm-slug>__sweep-<hash>/`\nconfig/surface_wave_sweep.example.yaml:1:version: surface_wave_sweep.v1\nconfig/surface_wave_sweep.example.yaml:6:    label: Default Milestone 10 reference parameters\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
